      "text": "Bet to warra Altari/kas ta KUNGA Preekycha bija/ to nozeble wiꞥſch no ta Naimma preeksch Galla/ starp (fawu) Altari/ un starp ta KUNGA Nammu/ un zehle to fahnis (fa-\nwu) Altari/prett Seemeta puffi.\n"
    },
