      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Kehnisch Akas pawebleja tam Preesteriam Uri-\njafam/ fazzidams: Us to leeln Altari buhs tew eededsinaht to Dedsamo-Uppuri Rihta/ un to Ehdamo-Uppuri Wakara/ ir ta Kehniza Dedsamo- Uppuri/ un winna Ehdamo-Uppuri/ ir wiſſu Semmes Lauschu Dedsamo-Up-\npuri/ un winan Dserramo-Up-\npuri/ un tew buhs us to wiſſu Afint flazzinaht no teem De-\ndsamo-Uppureem/ un no teem zit-\nteem Uppureem/ bet par to war-\nta Altari es dohmaschu/ ko es darrischu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas Preesteris Urijas darrija pehz wiſſu/ ko tas keh-\nnisch Akas bij paweblejs.\n"
